  "response": "Civil status refers to an individual's legal standing in relation to marriage, partnership, or other personal relationships as recognized by law. It typically includes categories such as:\n\n1. Single\n2. Married\n3. Divorced\n4. Widowed\n5. Separated\n6. In a civil partnership\n7. Registered domestic partnership\n\nCivil status can affect various legal and social aspects of a person's life, including taxation, inheritance, healthcare decisions, and social benefits.",
